Package: pboted
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends:
 ${misc:Pre-Depends},
 adduser
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 lsb-base
Description: C++ implementation of I2P-Bote.
 I2P-Bote is a server-less Kademlia DHT-based email protocol.
 Interaction with the I2P network occurs through the SAMv3 interface (tested with i2pd and Java I2P).
